<h2>Network of Allies</h2>

<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-1217" title="Network of Allies" alt="" src="http://www.hacer.org/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/allies150x1501.jpg" width="150" height="150" />America was founded by individuals who were willing to risk their life for what they believed in. They not only possessed the courage to act, they possessed the character to know right from wrong.</p>
<p>The disunity we see all around us at home and on foreign shores can only be solved when enough leaders stand up for what is right and enough people follow them because they are people of true character.</p>
<p>&#8220;United We Stand, Divided We Fall&#8221; is about the importance of shared values and efforts.</p>
<p><em></em>HACER and its network of allies truly embody the core values of personal and economic liberty, limited government under the rule of law, and individual responsibility required for making the Americas a better place.</p>
<p>This is the complete list of our allied think tanks:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.acton.org/" target="_blank">Acton Institute</a> (USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.aipenet.com/" target="_blank">AIPE Carlos Ball</a> (Venezuela)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.andeslibres.com/" target="_blank">Andes Libres</a> (Peru)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.anfe.cr/" target="_blank">Asociacion Nacional de Fomento Economico</a> (Costa Rica)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.atlasusa.org/" target="_blank">Atlas Economic Research Foundation</a> (USA)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cedice.org.ve/" target="_blank">CEDICE</a> (Venezuela)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cees.org.gt/" target="_blank">Centro de Estudios Economicos y Sociales</a> (Guatemala)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.centrorevel.org.uy/" target="_blank">Centro de Estudios Jean François Revel</a> (Uruguay)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ceres-uy.org/" target="_blank">Centro de Estudios de la Realidad Economica y Social</a> (Uruguay)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.victimasdeargentina.org/" target="_blank">Centro de Estudios Legales contra el Terrorismo y sus Victimas</a> (Argentina)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.libertadyresponsabilidad.org/" target="_blank">Centro de Estudios Libertad y Responsabilidad</a> (Argentina)</li>
